 277          /*
 278           *--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 279           * void SPI_Setup(unsigned char ctrlCmd, unsigned char intrEnb, unsigned char baudrate, unsigned char slvS
             -el)
 280           * Purpose : Setup the SPI module and initiate SPI function.
 281           * Params  : ctrlCmd - control register value.
 282           *           intrEnb - interrupt source enabled bit.
 283           *           baudrate - a parameterto generate baudrate.
 284           *           slvSel - slave selection bit.
 285           * Returns : None.
